  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Sega Sports 1 is a Sega Mega Drive compilation containing three previously released Mega Drive sports games. It is similar to other Mega Drive compilations - Mega Games 1, Mega Games 2, Mega Games 3, Sonic Classics etc. Sega Sports 1 was only released in Europe in 1995.\n\nLike some other compilations by Sega (Master Games 1, Sega Ages: Volume 1), there was never a \"Sega Sports 2\".",
